title: In Plain Sight walkthrough - How to escape the Police - Watch Dogs
tags: ['in plain sight', 'how to escape the police', 'watch dogs', 'walkthrough', 'jam coms', 'wkz van driver']
description: What you need for the In Plain Sight mission is a lot of com jammers. Best way is to learn the Jam Coms skill from the Hacking tree because most likely you will need more than 5. Before you start the chase tag a waypoint on your map to a harbor and drive there after you take down the WKZ van driver. Use the com jammers whenever you are about to be scanned completely by ctOS on your way to the harbor. Once you board a boat make sure that you are far away from the shores and then stay put to be scanned by ctOS and start the police chase. A single helicopter will approach you immediately. Kill the sharpshooter riding at the side of it and the helicopter will go away. After its gone just get out of the police chase circle to finish the mission.

title: Como hacer un collar tejido con cadena  | JPaola
tags: ['DIY', 'Decorar', 'Como hacer', 'Manualidades', 'Paso a paso', 'Decoración', 'Tutoríal', 'Crafting', 'Cocina', 'Artesanía', 'Creativo', 'Step by step', 'JPaola', 'collar con cadena', 'collar con hilos', 'como tejer un collar', 'ideas de collar', 'como hacer un collar', 'collar de moda', 'collar de colores', 'collar facil de hacer', 'collar de hilos', 'collares 2015', 'collares 2016', 'collares 2017']
description:
Aprende como hacer este bonito collar de moda para una ocasión especial con este tutorial paso a paso.

Para este tutorial vamos a necesitar:

- 7 Hilos para bordar (6 colores diferentes, 1 color dorado o plateado)
- Pinza
- Tijeras
- Cadena (delgada o gruesa)
- 1 broche
- 4 argollas
- 1 aguja 

Paso a paso

1. Separamos cada uno de los hilos, se deben doblar a lo largo, a la medida en que queremos el collar. debemos tener en cuenta que el hilo dorado o plateado que vamos a utilizar lo debemos separa para tres grupos de hilos que vamos a formar.

2. Cada grupo esta formado por dos tonos mas el color dorado o plateado, separamos cada grupo en tres partes y hacemos una tranza, al finalizar envolvemos las puntas con cinta

3. Tomamos una argolla y enlazamos los hilos, apretando fuerte con la pinza, igual del otro lado, retiramos las cintas y cortamos el excedente. 

4. Enhebramos la aguja y aseguramos con un nudo el primer eslabón de la cadena, tomamos la trenza y empezamos a unirla a la cadena de extremo a extremo.

5. Utilizamos una argolla y la ajustamos en el primer y ultimo eslabón de la cadena.

6. Para terminar, ubicamos en un extremo el broche y lo unimos a una de las argollas.

Espero que lo disfrutes!!!

title: mirage jazz orchestra
description:
Mirage Jazz Orchestra' emerged on the jazz scene of Latvia in January 2004. Two passionate jazz musicians  trombonist Lauris Amantovs together with the saxophonist Deniss Pashkevich  decided to form a big band. Active and creative rehearsals have brought them appreciation of their music among jazz lovers across the country. The orchestra unites the very best Latvian Jazz musicians. Just to name a few  piano player Madars Kalnins, who is also an acclaimed composer, arranger and the leader of other jazz units.. Another distinguished band member is the trumpeter Ülo Ussenko who has been the leading trumpet player for many years in the famous Latvian Radio Big band just like the honorable alto sax player Ivars Birkāns, trumpet player Zigurds Linde. The repertoire is comprised of modern jazz compositions. December 2004 was a new turn for the band as the young vocalist Intars Busulis  the winner of international competitions and Jazz Awards including Grand Prix of Sony Jazz Stage 2004 and the Grand Prix of the Singers' Contest 'Novaya Volna 2005' joined the band. The most valuable gain to the band has been their close cooperation with the legendary trumpet player, arranger and composer, Europe wide distinguished musician Gunars Rozenbergs. His skillfully formed arrangements make the orchestra sound in ever-new colors. It is hard to believe they are not a full big band cast. The Mirage orchestra has performed at Klaipeda Jazz Festival 2005 in Lithuania, 'Rigas Ritmi 2005' festival and Saulkrasti Jazz 2005, 2006 in Latvia as well as various other venues.


The band members: Gunars Rozenbergs (art director and arranger), Lauris Amantovs (trombone), Deniss Pashevichs (sax; flute), Ivars Birkans (sax; flute), Indrikis Veitners (sax; clarinet), Raivo Stašāns (sax, flute), Űlo Ussenko (trumpet), Normunds Piesis (trumpet), Gints Stepanovs (trumpet), Zigurds Linde (trumpet), Karlis Tortuzis (trombone), Madars Kalnins (piano), Viktors Zelenkovs (bass), Raimonds Kalniņš (percussions).

Band's manager Janis Daugulis.

title: Rosenkreuzstilette - The Devil (Palace II)
description:
"Is not the same calling the Devil than seeing the Devil arrive"

A video of me falling upward through the Iris Palace II, The Garden of Chaos.

RKS is a Mega Man clone which copy the most important aspect of Mega Man. The thing that makes Mega Man, Mega Man. No, not the copy of power. I mean The Devil.

Let's cruise swiftly through the stage. This stage is very beautiful. Again we see a gimmick, making this one of the most interesting (and frustrating) stage in the game. The Garden of Chaos (a.k.a. The Garden of Time and Space) gimmick is the switching of the gravitational force. Every time you pass through one of those waterfalls, you'll gravitational force will become that of the force acting on the waterfall. In other words, if the waterfall is falling upward, you'll fall upward. If it's falling downward, you'll fall downward. The gimmick by itself is nothing spectacular, but there are some jumps and some tricks that become irritating with the gimmick. Like the upward fall through spikes...

But the main entrée of this stage is the boss fight. During the final portion of the stage, you start seeing a Beholder in the background, watching and judging your every movement. This alone tells you that the following battle is gonna be hard. And true enough, when you reach the boss room, you are presented with the obligatory Devil any Mega Man game MUST have. Unless you are an actual Mega Man game. In that case you can get away without having a Devil.

RKS's Devil is the Deviled Egg (or Mold Devil before the real name was revealed). If you are a Mega Man fan, you know what to expect from this battle. If not, let me tell you some history. The first Devil in a Mega Man game was the Yellow Devil in Mega Man 1. And it was HARD. The fact that people abused the limitations of the game to beat the damn thing is a testament to its difficulty. The boss was so iconic that a couple of other games have similar boss fights and it's expected of Mega Man clones to have a Devil-ish boss. For example, both RKS have a Devil as a boss fight and MegaMari (the Touhou Mega Man clone) gives Suika the honor of being the Devil of that game.

The Devils' pattern are actually very simple, but for normal gamers it can be pretty hard. Elegance in simplicity and all that. In this case, to further establish the glamour of this boss fight, the Deviled Egg enters the battle doing its pattern. Like all Devils, the pattern consist of pieces of boss flying in a static pattern towards you. Either jump or slide to avoid them. This pattern is ALWAYS the same. If you get hit, you can quickly take this opportunity to hide behind the spot where the Devil was and avoid the rest of the pattern. Then the boss open his singular eye, shoots a bullets, and sends piece at you in the exact same pattern. Rinse and repeat. All Devils have this pattern, but with small variations.

In the case of Deviled Egg, this small variation is the gravity switching of the stage. After hitting Desperation Mode, the Devil will sometimes switch the gravity after each attack. The pattern is still the same, but the new perspective can prove disorienting. The Deviled Egg is weak to the Tempest of Love, Liebessturm. You need four Liebessturm to put it down, and you must time them so that the hitbox of Liebessturm connects with the Devil's eye is open. Otherwise you will miss. If you're like me, chances are you don't have the Liebessturm charges to beat him. Or maybe you do. In any case, hitting with the Soul Rifle before Desperation Mode should save you enough Liebessturm to finish it quickly before the fight becomes dangerous.

And with this, only two more videos to tackle. Yay!

title: Chocolate Fried Chicken Recipe | Eat the Trend
tags: ['POPSUGAR Food', 'YumSugarTV', 'easy recipes', 'cooking basics', 'dessert recipes', 'food', 'food tutorials', 'Eat the Trend', 'Chocolate Fried Chicken', 'food hybrid', 'food trends', 'food how to']
description:
When Adam Fleischman, the guy behind Umami's Monte Cristo Burger and 800 Degrees Pizzeria, announced that he was making chocolate fried chicken, we knew we had to try it. While you'll still have to buy a ticket to LA to try his original ChocoChicken, our test kitchen whipped up a recipe that is lip-smacking good and a testament to chocolate's versatility (it's not just for sweets!). 

Chocolate Fried Chicken
From Nicole Iizuka, POPSUGAR Food

{INGREDIENTS}

For chocolate buttermilk brine:
1 quart buttermilk
2 tablespoons cocoa powder
1 teaspoon salt
1 teaspoon pepper
1 teaspoon cayenne pepper
1 teaspoon garlic, minced
12 to 15 chicken tenders

For dry batter:
1 cup all-purpose flour
1/2 cup cornstarch
1/2 cup cocoa powder
1/2 teaspoon salt
1/2 teaspoon pepper
1/4 teaspoon cinnamon
1/4 teaspoon nutmeg
1/4 teaspoon cayenne pepper

Neutral oil, such as canola or peanut, for frying

For Tabasco honey:
1/4 cup honey
1 teaspoon tabasco sauce

{DIRECTIONS}

Make the brine: In a large bowl or heavy-duty resealable plastic bag, mix together the buttermilk, cocoa powder, salt, pepper, cayenne pepper, and garlic.

Add chicken tenders, and make sure they are submerged. Cover and refrigerate for at least 12 hours, up to 48 hours.

Make the dry batter: In another large bowl, mix together the flour, cornstarch, cocoa powder, salt, pepper, cinnamon, nutmeg, and cayenne pepper.

Fry the chicken: Remove the chicken from the brine, and dredge the chicken in the flour mixture. Shake off any excess.

Heat the oil in a heavy-bottomed dutch oven or electric deep fryer to 350°F. Add chicken to the oil in batches, and cook for 6 to 7 minutes, turning occasionally, until the tenders are cooked through. Drain off excess oil by laying chocolate fried chicken on a paper-towel-lined plate.

Make the Tabasco honey: Mix together honey and tabasco, until combined. Serve with warm chocolate fried chicken.

title: Kingdom Hearts 358/2 days coming to North America in mid-2009
description:
Kingdom Hearts 358/2 days is coming out in mid 2009 for North America. 

That arcticle says:Fans of Disney-Crossover series Kingdom Hearts can finally rest easy: publisher Square Enix has confirmed that the DS installment of their hit-action RPG franchise will be coming to North America in mid-2009. 

Developed by h.a.n.d. (maker of Final Fantasy Fables: Chocobos Dungeon) and titled Kingdom Hearts 358/2 Days, the sagas latest chapter takes place following the events of 2004 GBA Game Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories and star Roxas (essentially a clone of seires protagonist Sora) and his cohorts in the mysterious Organization XIII. Despite the change in heroes, the gameplay remains essentially the same as in the main Kingdom Hearts titles: youll still travel to worlds based on various Disney movies (such as Beauty and the Beast, Aladdin, Hercules, and the Nightmare Before Christmas) and use physical attacks and magic spells to fight evil Heartless in real-time battle.

For the first time in the series, youll also be able to team up with friends in a four player co-op mode that lets you each control a different member of Organization XIII. Additionally, you can expect extragavant cut-scenes, quality voice work, and a plot that reveals what happened between Kingdom Hearts and Kingdom Hearts 2.

title: Profecias del 2012 - El dia en que todo cambiará....
description:
Las Profecías - www.ProfeciasPara2012.com

La mayor parte del mundo civilizado sabe todo acerca de las predicciones contenidas en el Libro de las Revelaciones, dentro de la Biblia. Por supuesto, no hay una fecha exacta del fin del mundo en los versos del Apocalipsis. Sin embargo, hay predicciones mucho más conocidas que no se encuentran en la Biblia y que aseguran que estos acontecimientos sucederán. Pensar que la Biblia es la única fuente de conocimiento sobre el fin del mundo, tal vez no es un pensamiento acorde al desarrollo intelectual del siglo 21.
La fecha del 21 de diciembre 2012 surge del calendario maya. Muchas personas piensan que sólo porque la civilización maya dejó de existir hace siglos, esta predicción carece de sentido, y argumentan que esos cálculos no coinciden con la línea de tiempo de nuestro calendario. Es posible que a lo largo de la historia hayan cambiado la procesión de días, pero la humanidad no puede cambiar el movimiento de las estrellas y de los planetas. Un gran número de otros eventos astrológicamente predichos también se encontraban incluidos en el calendario maya y han sucedido en los tiempos que ellos estipularon. 

Sería muy necio para una persona inteligente como usted desacreditar el vasto conocimiento de un pueblo, simplemente porque su momento en la Tierra fue hace mucho tiempo.

Los mayas tenían una increíble habilidad con las matemáticas y la astrología. Ellos crearon no sólo un calendario para 3500 años, sino también una calculadora matemática. La fecha final del calendario maya se determina utilizando dicha calculadora y estudiando las actividades de los astros, y esta y otras predicciones mayas se han puesto a prueba con modernos programas de computación usados por instituciones prestigiosas en todo el mundo.
Las predicciones de la civilización Maya pueden parecer prehistóricas, sin embargo, su gente poseía la capacidad de construir estructuras que el hombre moderno no puede.
Los Mayas, de la misma forma que otras civilizaciones antiguas en diferentes partes del mundo, construyeron edificios de piedra de una manera que aún hoy no podemos comprender.

De acuerdo con las previsiones contenidas en el calendario maya, se da la situación de encontrarnos con que el mismo conocimiento e información que ellos tenían, están también presentes en el calendario azteca. Hay quienes creen que los aztecas copiaron el calendario maya, sin embargo, no hay pruebas fehacientes de que así sea.

La predicción de que el fin del mundo está llegando también está reflejada en las profecías del I-Ching, de Merlín, de Cybil, de la Madre Shipton, de las tribus de nativos americanos, de la Biblia y de Nostradamus. Si estas fuentes de información le parecen demasiado anticuadas, tal vez el programa Web Bot le será de mayor utilidad y será más efectivo en su mente moderna.

Hay significados muy importantes relacionados a la fecha del 21 de diciembre que ya son conocidos en todo el mundo. Este es el día del equinoccio que marca el comienzo del invierno para el hemisferio norte y del verano para el hemisferio sur. En Astrología, la fecha 21 de diciembre de 2012 es la fecha en la que comienza la Era de Acuario. 

Esto marca el inicio de una nueva era, no sólo para el planeta Tierra, sino para todo nuestro sistema solar.

description:
Before he was Kool Kojak, Allan Grigg and his brother built their own drum set out of tape and pvc pipes and created their own recordings using their boombox. It was the start of a lifelong quest to make the hip hop sounds that inspired him from childhood. His tenacity led him to New York where he interned at legendary hip hop studios, saved for years to get his prized MPC drum machine, and made musical friendships that would lead to number one hit songs around the world.

Kool Kojak's success is no fluke. He works hard but he plays hard, not afraid to push himself into experimentation and find his own sound. His reputation and credits have led him to work with artists like Flo Rida, Nicki Minaj, Britney Spears, Ke$ha, and many many more.

title: Sonic Advance 3 No Emerald Walkthrough Part 14 (Finale)
description:
Part 14: Trilogy ending...
 
G-Mel 5 and Final Boss
 
This is it... The end of a era. No more Sonic Advance games. :( BUT I will be going back to the Genesis era to play Sonic 3-D Blast! Stay tuned for that!
 
Oh and make sure you grab your unlocked Cream for these bosses. ;)
 
Miniboss: G-Mel 5: OK, I really did make a mountain out of a molehill here, lol! This is WAY easier then I made it look. You already know how to dodge the older attacks he has and how to hit him.. so I'll just cover the new attacks. When he does the spiral missle attack, just jump between them from the edge of the screen. It's not as hard as you expect actually because you can see where the missles are going. When he does the aerial dash missle attack, all the missles go for you,.. Just spin dash away from them. Easy.
 
Boss: Egg Smasher: OK This is it! The FINAL boss! (for non-emerald collectors, lol!) From anywhere really, you can jump up with cream and throw Cheese at Eggman for a hit... That's it really, lol! Well, there are a few attacks to dodge. 
 
When he hovers his hands upwards... he's going to smash them down. stay on one of the middle platforms and be ready to spin dash to the opposite one if he is about to take down your platform. DO NOT attack Eggman when he is swinging his hands down... you may get hit down in the hole.
 
When his hands are off to the sides and he plays Pong with himself, you can just jump on the balls to get up to him and be away from the other balls to hit him with Cheese. Simple.
 
When he spins his hands with palms out to theleft and right sides, he's going to arm thrust you... This one... I am not sure how to dodge, lol! I think you have to spin dash jump out of the way... but I only got it to work a few times. :P

I don't think there's anything more to cover... If I remember something, I'll add it in.

This is a "No Emerald" walkthrough, meaning that I did not collect the Chaos Emeralds.
 
Enjoy!

title: Jane Doe - Hermione/Draco
description:
This is the exact same video but I made it widescreen and I sorted the text out as it was kinda unclear before.

Hermione was always there for Draco and would do anything for him, they weren't officially dating but they both loved each other but remained close friends until one day Hermione was killed, by Draco himself!. *gasp*, but of course he is the only one that knew.

We start at Hermione's funeral (which is why Draco is in a suit) and Draco is remembering where it all started... when they came back from the summer holidays, Hermione was cheerful as usual but Draco was different, he was rude and mean to Hermione, Hermione puts up with it but she is sure that something is wrong with her friend, but every time she asks him about it he gets angry with her and tells her to stay out of it.

We then go back to present day where Draco is now trying to live a normal life which he is finding impossible due to the guilt over what he did, it doesn't help matters when he starts to see Hermione's face everywhere he looks as he is being haunted by Hermione's ghost, then one day in care of magical creatures he point's out Hermione's ghost to everyone, only to find that they cant see her and that he is the only one that can. He tries to talk things over and apologise to Hermione for what he did, but Hermione doesn't buy it, there are then some of Hermiones memories of her still believing that something is wrong with Draco, even though no one else seems to think so and when Draco eventually gives in and tells Hermione the truth, that over the summer he became a Death Eater, Hermione of course is horrified, it is at that moment that Draco realises that he shouldn't have told her, that now Voldermort will find out about his closeness to Hermione (a Mudblood) and that he will kill her, so he makes a snap decision to kill her himself before Voldermort can, a decision he instantly regrets.

Back to present day and Draco is still haunted by both Hermiones ghost and his memories of her. His sadness increases when he is looking through a photo album and finds some pictures of himself and Hermione at the Yule Ball, later on in the common room when he is thinking about Hermione, he remembers the time when they were very young and Draco told Hermione they would be 'Together Forever' and he realises that there is only one solution to his problem...


Songs: 
Funeral: When youre gone by Avril Lavigne
Main: Jane Doe by Within Temptation

Black and White: Memories
Colour: Present day
Red Tinted: When he is killing Hermione
Bluey/Pinky Colour: Hermiones ghost

title: How to Make Classic MACARONI SALAD Recipe
tags: ['classic macaroni salad recipe', 'classic macaroni salad', 'pennsylavania dutch', 'food', 'macaroni salad', 'macaroni', 'macaroni salad recipe', 'the best macaroni salad recipe', 'amish macaroni salad recipe', 'amish macaroni salad', 'macaroni salad recipe with egg', 'recipes', 'homemade macaroni salad', 'tuna macaroni salad', 'recipe', 'how to make homemade macaroni salad', 'cooking', 'how to cook macaroni salad', 'tess cooks 4u', 'how to make pasta salad', 'how to make', 'macaroni salad with egg', 'macaroni egg salad']
description:
Learn how to make Homemade Macaroni Salad that is a Holiday Favorite.  My childhood macaroni salad recipe and I will share with you in my kitchen.  Come along and enjoy.


How to make Holiday Favorite MACARONI SALAD

INGREDIENTS:

1 pound cooked macaroni pasta - I used Cellentani pasta
1 cup finely diced celery
1 cup finely dice pickles - Used Clausen kosher dill
1/4 cup finely diced red onion
6 finely chopped hard boiled eggs
1 cup mayonnaise
1 tbsp Dijon mustard
1 tbsp sugar
1 tbsp apple cider vinegar
1 tbsp extra virgin olive oil
1/8 tsp kosher salt
1/4 tsp black pepper
1/4 tsp celery seed

Mix cooled cooked pasta to large mixing bowl. Add
chopped eggs, chopped celery, pickles, and onion.
Mix well.

Add seasonings, sugar, vinegar, oil, Dijon mustard,
and mayonnaise.
Mix well.

Refrigerate for 3-4 hours or overnight is better.

Can add flaked tuna into the mixture. 
Even some olives or fresh parsley is good. 

A childhood favorite. Enjoy.

description:
Zvex Double Rock 

Shop Effects & Pedals here: https://bit.ly/3hOvvdV

This pedal was originally designed for J.Mascis of Dinosaur Jr. He requested two Box of Rock pedals in one box with two stomp switches (without the boosts). He uses that regularly on stage now, but we did one (or two) better with the one we're releasing to the public... we made it so you can adjust the sub frequencies (like the DistortronTM), and you can convert either channel to a Super Hard-OnTM. In this way, you can configure the pedal to be two Distortrons cascaded, two Super Hard-Ons cascaded (like a Super Duper 2-in-1TM), or a Box of RockTM with boost, or a Super Hard-OnTM going into a Box of RockTM. Distortion/boost heaven!

Guitar played: Gibson '59 Reissue Les Paul Standard Cherry Sunburst 2008

title: PlayStation 4 - Así se jugará a PS4, según Sony
tags: ['19/06/2013', 'según Sony', 'Juegosep', 'tech', 'videogames', '2013', '06/19/2013', 'PlayStation 4 - Así se jugará a PS4', 'gadget', 'videojuegos']
description:
Sony tenía preparada una bomba en el E3. La compañía no enseñó demasiados juegos exclusivos para PlayStation 4, pero sí contó con un gran apoyo de las third parties y además se lo puso muy complicado a Microsoft con el precio: 399 euros, frente a los 499 de Xbox One. También se mostró por primera vez la máquina, tras las críticas de la presentación de febrero en la que no se vio, y se lanzó una impresionante pulla a la competencia: PS4 no necesitará conectarse una vez al día y no restringirá de ninguna forma el mercado de segunda mano.

title: Windy and Warm - Solo Fingerstyle Guitar by Frédéric Mesnier
tags: ['Guitar', 'Acoustic', 'fmguitar', 'classical guitar', 'fingerstyle guitar', 'Chet Atkins (Musical Artist)', 'Windy and Warm', 'Marcel Dadi (Guitarist)', 'Tommy Emmanuel (Musical Artist)', 'Guitar Cover', 'Acoustic Guitar', 'Solo', 'Acoustic Cover']
description:
Sheet Music: https://shop.fredericmesnier.com/sheet-music/sheet-music-windy-and-warm
Music: https://shop.fredericmesnier.com/music/music-windy-and-warm

Details & Credits:
Composer: John D. Loudermilk
Performer: Frédéric Mesnier
Guitar: Model Concert L by Maurice Dupont - (France)
Strings: Savarez - Alliance Corum
Tuning: Standard
Microphones: Sennheiser MK4

This famous standard by John Loudermilk was made popular by Chet Atkins in the 60's. It's one of the very first songs I learnt.  This version is a personal mix from various guitarists (Marcel Dadi, Chet Atkins, Tommy Emmanuel...) I increased the tempo and put a capo second fret. I played this piece hundreds of times and still have fun with it. Thanks for watching.

Fred

title: Dr. Brain: Action Reaction
description:
Ironically, this is my first HD video. Action Reaction is a problem-solving game created by Knowledge Adventure. Using the three laws of physics, switch flipping, rocket turrets, and the "helping hand" to knock out guards, the player battles through 45 levels to capture the evil Dr. Craven. Fun game, I just rediscovered it after ten years. Aren't `99 graphics fantastic? All those circles with squared edges...  

Actually the graphics are surprisingly good for being over a decade old. Still, just like Battlezone (the '98 computer game which has a larger following) it is becoming increasingly difficult to play on modern systems.

김연아, 양준혁 등 올림픽스타들이 함께하는 2013평창동계 스페셜올림픽 D-100 성공기원 '청계천 걷기대회'가 21일 오후 서울 청계천 광장에서 열렸다.

이날 행사는 2013평창동계 스페셜올림픽 조직위원회(위원장 나경원)가 내년 1월 강원도 강릉과 평창 등지에서 열릴 스페셜올림픽 개막 100일을 앞두고 대회의 성공개최를 기념하기위해 마련됐다.

이번 행사에는 김연아, 구본길, 김지연, 김정환, 심권호, 양준혁 등이 참석해 청계천 광장을 출발해 청계천로를 왕복하는 3km 구간의 '걷기대회'를 진행했다.

또한 이병우 이적이 부른 2013평창동계 스페셜올림픽 공식주제가가 발표됐으며, 울랄라세션의 공연이 진행돼 시민들의 큰 호응을 얻었다.  

한편 2013평창동계 스페셜올림픽은 전 세계 지적발달 장애인들에게 지속적인 스포츠 훈련기회를 제공해 운동능력과 사회 적응력을 향상시켜 생산적인 사회구성원으로 인정받도록 하는 데 기여하고자 하는 국제스포츠대회다. 오는 2013년 1월 29일부터 2월 5일까지 8일간 강원도 평창 및 강릉 일대에서 열린다.

title: Seward Mountain
description: A day hike of Seward Mountain in the Adirondack High Peaks on 21 November 2009. Seward Mountain is one of the four peaks of the Seward Range. The Seward Range can be accessed via Corey's Road just north of Tupper Lake or via the trail to Duck Pond from Upper Works. Seward Mountain is a trail-less High Peak although has a pretty well-defined herdpath to the summit from the Ward Brook truck trail.

ＧＨＥＮＫＩ　アイソロープ・エレメンタル・コリオ　香取大志
tags: ['ＧＨＥＮＫＩ', '香取大志', 'hiroshi', 'katori', '肥満', 'ダイエット', '痩せる', '腹筋']
description:
アイソロープ・エレメンタル・コリオ
Iso-Rope Elemental Choreo (IREC)

ＩＲＥＣ（アイレック）は、アイソロープを用いた舞踊スタイルの体操です。４種の元素（エレメント）である「地・水・火・風」を主要モチーフとし、それら４元素の働きと「空」（空間）をさまざまなムーブで表現します。総合的な体操である ＩＲＥＣ では、各ムーブにエクササイズとしての意味があり、それぞれが違った角度からカラダ全体を活性化させて代謝を高めます。また各ムーブにあてられた名称によって、自然の中のシーンを想像でき、伸びやかな運動と正しい動きが身につきやすいようプログラムされています。朝の体操、気分転換、毎日のメインエクササイズとしても有効な ＩＲＥＣは、ＧＨＥＮＫＩの練習生にとって大きな習得目標の１つとなるものです。

ＩＲＥＣ 各ムーブの名称
前奏 ：　黎明
空 ：　地平　世界　仰天
地 ：　鎮座　隆起　平原
水 ：　静湖　大波　深淵
火 ：　昇焔　渦焔　灼炉
風 ：　循気　嵐気　朝凪
締め ：　仰天

GHENKI創始者・インストラクター：香取大志（かとり・ひろし）

１９７５年５月８日生、千葉県出身。
１０代の頃から従来の筋力トレーニングに疑問を持ち、独自の概念を基底にカラダづくり­を始める。自然や動物の在り方、武道などを参考にカラダ本来の形と働きを解釈、人体を­「機能を有する１つの複合的力学体系」と観察し長年にわたる実践を経て、「体型づくり­と維持のカギは日々の生活の中にこそある」という結論に至る。
　ジムでのトレーニングやダンスの訓練の経験は全くのゼロだが、２０代を通して滞在した­ロサンゼルス、ロンドン、イスラエルではファッションモデルやダンサーなど芸能活動に­従事。香取大志の概念や実践法が、体型づくりと身体機能の向上に非常に適している事実­の証明となっている。
　西洋・中東・東洋を通し見て「世界中のほとんどの人々が、自分のカラダが持っている本­当のポテンシャルに気づいていないし活かしていない」という事実を痛感。世の中の人々­がそのポテンシャルを開花させ、健康で元気に満ち、自分自身の外見にも満足してもらい­たいという願いから、３５歳にして自身の実践法を体系化、誰にでも手軽に始めて簡単に­続けられる「ＧＨＥＮＫＩ」を創始。現在、インストラクターとして定期ワークショップ­を開催している。
　また、ケンブリッジ英語検定ＣＰＥ（特級）、日本語教師資格を有する言語エキスパート­でもある。ケンブリッジ大認定英語教師・通訳・映像翻訳家。

使用曲「Elements Awakened」　作曲：香取大志

http://blog.livedoor.jp/ghenki/

title: Fake school meeting turns into $400 surprise for La Joya ISD teacher
tags: ['KGBT', 'Action 4 News', 'Rio Grande Valley', 'Barrington Broadcasting', 'Pay it 4ward', 'Pronto Insurance', 'La Joya', 'Teachers', 'Ryan Wolf']
description:
A veteran La Joya Independent School District teacher at Clinton Elementary School gets the surprise of her career. 
            Mercedes Silva is rewarded on Pay it 4Ward for her selfless acts of kindness.
            Co-workers say she uses her own money to buy shirts for students, brings breakfast for others on long days, drives colleagues to work so they can save on gas, and makes home visits for students in need.
            She does it all without expecting anything in return.
            Mrs. Silva is called back to Clinton Elementary School for a fake meeting on Thursday afternoon.
            Action 4 News is in the library where Mercedes thinks the meeting is at.
            She believes the camera crew is there to interview the superintendent about summer programs.
            Action 4's Ryan Wolf strikes up conversation with Mercedes as the two sit alone in an area.         
            Ryan: Was it a good year?  I heard a lot of good things happened at Clinton.
            Mercedes: Yes.  It's a good school to be in.
            Mercedes doesn't realize a camera is recording the conversation from a distance.
            Ryan: We're really excited to be here but it's not just for the superintendent.
            Mercedes: Oh really?  For Clinton?
            Ryan: It's for Clinton and somebody else.
            Mercedes: Who?
            Little does she know, dozens of her colleagues are waiting outside the library to share with her what an incredible person she is.
            The Pay it 4Ward surprise begins to unfold.
            Ryan: I'm here because of you.
            Mercedes: Me?
            Ryan: Because of you.  
            Mercedes: You're funny.
            Ryan: It's the incredible work you do for the students.
            Mercedes: You're crazy.
            Ryan: And for what you do for staff at Clinton Elementary.  Paula come on in.
            Mercedes: Who?
            Paula Garcia is a co-worker who nominated Mercedes for the Pay it 4Ward prize on valleycentral.com.
            Her online submission talks about how she's one-of-a-kind, inspiring and giving without expecting anything in return.
            Paula enters the library along with other staff members who are in on the surprise.
            Paula: You mean so much to everybody.  You really do.  You're very kind, caring and big-hearted and we wanted to reward you with something special... on behalf of Pronto Insurance and Action 4 News, we would like to Pay it 4Ward.  Here's $400!
            Applause breaks out in the room.
            It's a room that's clearly filled with love and support.
            Mercedes begins to cry.
            She calls this moment one of the best of her career, which includes 2 teacher of the year awards over her 17 years.
            "I do it out of my heart and I do things for the kids because I love my kids," she said.  "I don't do it for the reward."
            Her reward is the new pre-paid Pronto MasterCard, as company spokesperson Domingo Reyna explains.
            "We're proudly presenting to you this $400 Pronto pre-paid MasterCard that you can utilize anytime, reload and even open a savings account with," he said.
            The staff at the elementary is more like family, according to Principal Martin Munoz.
            He says honoring Mercedes' dedication on Action 4 News is a thrill for everyone.
            "Clinton Elementary is very appreciative to the Pay it 4Ward program," he said.  "She's an awesome teacher."
            A teacher who credits her upbringing as the reason for always wanting to give back.
            Her advice to others working with kids?
            "Give 'em all your heart," she said.  "The kids deserve it.  Without the kids we're nothing."

title: Кэрролл, Алиса - Лучшая песня о любви- Alice & Lewis Carroll
description:
Льюис Кэрролл и Алиса Лидделл Харгривз в фантазии под песню "Лучшая песня о любви" группы "Високосный год". Фрагменты советских мультфильмов "Алиса в стране чудес", "Алиса в Зазеркалье". Alice Liddell & Lewis Carroll in a fantasy vid, Soviet animated cartoons and old photos used.

The lyrics in translation (Russian band 'Leap Year'='Visokosny God')

Ok, now sit down and listen to my story.
He never bore ill will to her.
He never wanted to be engraved upon her heart,
to deprive her of innocent sleep.
At weekends he brought her sweets,
he contemplated the lines in her palm.
He never knew a greater joy
than to address her by her first name.

She was about 36
when he peacefully passed away.
She had not managed
to dial his simple number for the last time.
And, for the first time she was now bringing him flowers,
two bright white lilies,
to show that no one else could call her by her first name
the way he did.

She was about 76
when she passed away.
She had not been afraid of death
she had been dreaming about it.
Imagine, she would sit by the window
watching watching watching the blue sky intently.
Thinking: when I die I will meet him there,
and he will call me by my first name.

How funny the life turned out to be.
Still... what could be more beautiful
than to be sitting on a cloud, your legs hanging in the air,
calling each other by your first names.

Текст песни
Так вот, теперь сиди и слушай -
Он не желал ей зла,
Он не хотел запасть ей в душу
И тем лишить ее сна.
Он приносил по выходным ей сладости,
Читал в ее ладонях линии,
И он не знал на свете большей радости,
Чем называть ее по имени.

Ей было где-то тридцать шесть,
Когда он очень тихо помер,
Ей даже не пришлось успеть
В последний раз набрать его несложный номер.
Но в первый раз несла она ему цветы:
Две ярко-белых лилии
В знак, что более никто, кроме него,
Так не называл ее по имени.

И было ей семьдесят шесть,
Когда ее самой не стало.
Нет, не страшила ее смерть,
Скорей, она о ней мечтала.
Бывало, знаете ли, сядет у окна
И смотрит, смотрит, смотрит в небо синее -
Дескать, когда умру, я встречу его там,
и вновь тогда он назовет меня по имени.

Какая, в сущности, смешная вышла жизнь,
Хотя... что может быть красивее,
Чем сидеть на облаке и, свесив ножки вниз,
Друг друга называть по имени?

CLIP DESCRIPTION:
Hit men (Tobin Bell, Dean Norris) pursue Mitch (Tom Cruise).

FILM DESCRIPTION:
In this drama, based on the best-selling novel by John Grisham, Mitch McDeer (Tom Cruise) is a young man from a poor Southern family who has struggled through Harvard Law School to graduate fifth in his class. Mitch is entertaining offers from major firms in New York and Chicago, but when Memphis-based Bendini, Lambert, & Locke offer him a 20 percent higher salary than the best offer he's received, in addition to an enticing variety of perks and fringe benefits, he decides to sign on and remain in the South. Mitch's wife, Abby (Jeanne Tripplehorn), warns him that the deal sounds almost too good to be true, but it's not until after several weeks of working with Avery Tolar (Gene Hackman) that Mitch discovers that the vast majority of BL&L's business is tied to organized crime, with crime boss Joey Morolto (Paul Sorvino) using the firm to launder Mafia money. FBI agents Wayne Tarrance (Ed Harris) and F. Denton Voyles (Steven Hill) try to blackmail Mitch into helping them make a case against the firm, while BL&L's "security director" William Devasher (Wilford Brimley) is blackmailing him to do as he's told after Mitch foolishly allows himself to be seduced by a prostitute hired by the firm. The Firm was adapted for the screen by acclaimed playwright David Rabe and features performances by Hal Holbrook, Holly Hunter, and Gary Busey.

The actual Scotch game, or better Scotch opening, is really a chess opening that begins with
1. e4 e5

Ercole del Rio, inside their 1750 treatise Sopra il giuoco degli Scacchi, Osservazioni pratiche d'anonimo Autore Modense (On the action involving Chess, realistic Findings simply by a good private Modenese Author), ended up being the 1st writer to cover what's at this point known as the particular Scotch Opening. The actual opening obtained its identify coming from a letters fit inside 1824 concerning Edinburgh as well as London. The opening had lost preference between the stronger players given the fact that you release the tension early on in the  game, but with that said modern day grandmasters like Timman and Kasparov rejuvenated the opening while employing it in their games.

He also discusses the highs and lows Thorin will go through in the upcoming movie.

In the second film of The Hobbit trilogy, Bilbo Baggins (Martin Freeman) continues his journey with the Wizard Gandalf (Ian McKellen) and thirteen Dwarves, led by Thorin Oakenshield (Richard Armitage) on an epic quest to reclaim the lost Dwarf Kingdom of Erebor.

In this installment, they must face the dragon Smaug (voiced by Benedict Cumberbatch) in order to help the Dwarves return to their rightful home.

description:
Old school classic. I didn't have the original for my SNES anymore...which I would have rather done more but the Game Boy Advanced version and the Super Nintendo version are almost identical anyway....good enough. Great game. Enjoy it...watch the whole thing and Subscribe. 

I found every secret bonus room on each level and finished the game only missing some of the snapshots exclusive to this version of the game.

FAQ:
Q: Did you do this on an emulator?

A: Nope, did this on my Gamecube. I bought a device a long time ago called "Game Boy Player" that you connect to your Gamecube and allows you to play GBA games on your Cube.

Q:What's the difference between this game and the Super Nintendo version?

A: Not a whole lot. There's a few extra mini-games in it and the graphics on the SNES version are better. No real changes to the actual levels that I know of.

title: Killzone HD Designation Demolition Trophy Guide
description: To obtain this trophy you must destroy 3 Helghast Towers with the BDL-23 Dovhat. The BDL-23 Dohvat is automatically put into your inventory at the stat of Mission 1 on Chapter 8. Instead of using it for the tanks and APC's in the mission simply keep it to destroy the towers as it only has a limited charge. The towers are located very close to each other throughout the level. You will reach the first tower after the area with multiple APC's and a tank simply equip the BDL-23 and lase underneath the tower. The next tower is located a little further down the road simply make your way through the level there will be another APC as well as a group of enemies just before the next tower. when you turn the corner and continue round another corner you will see the second tower lase underneath it again and wait for it to be destroyed. The final tower is around the next corner shoot the APC gunner and proceed round the corner lase underneath this final tower and the trophy will unlock. It is also worth noting that you can simply return to the last checkpoint and destroy the same tower 3 times for the trophy.

title: Recette de ravioles et foie gras à l'huile de truffe blanche, bouillon de volaille
description:
Recette en vidéo de L'atelier des Chefs 
 
Ravioles garnies de morceaux de foie gras et parfumées à la truffe blanche, accompagnées d'un bouillon de volaille crémé.

 X 6 Personnes            20 Min

Lobe(s) de foie gras de canard : 1/2 pièce(s)  Aileron(s) de poulet : 200 gramme(s) 
Feuille(s) de pâte à raviole : 48 pièce(s)  
Huile de truffe blanche : 3 centilitre(s) 
oeuf(s)pour dorure : 1 pièce(s) 

Pour le bouillon :
Oignon(s) : 1 pièce(s)  
Carotte(s) : 1 pièce(s) 
Persil plat : 3 branche(s)  
Crème liquide entière : 10 centilitre(s) 
Fleur de sel : 6 Pincée(s)  
Poivre en grain : 5 gramme(s) 
Gros sel : 10 gramme(s)  
Arômate(s) ail, thym, laurier : 1 pièce(s) 
Moulin à poivre : 6 Tour(s) 


Recette : Raviole de foie gras à l'huile de truffe blanche, bouillon de volaille

Éplucher l'oignon et le couper en 4. Éplucher la carotte et l'émincer en grosses lamelles.

Dans une cocotte, mettre les carcasses de volaille ou les ailerons et les recouvrir d'eau froide à 3 cm au-dessus. Porter à ébullition et écumer les impuretés. Ajouter la garniture aromatique : ail, carotte, oignon, tige de persil plat, thym et laurier, puis assaisonner de poivre concassé et de fleur de sel. Cuire au minimum 30 min à feu doux.
Passer le tout dans une passoire et ajouter la crème liquide, puis rectifier l'assaisonnement et réserver.

Couper le foie gras en morceaux de 30 g et l'assaisonner de fleur de sel, de poivre du moulin et d'huile de truffe blanche.
Étaler les pâtes à raviole et poser le foie gras dessus, badigeonner le pourtour de dorure puis refermer la raviole avec l'autre feuille de pâte. Découper ensuite à l'emporte-pièce pour obtenir une belle raviole (attention à bien la refermer et à ne pas laisser d'air à l'intérieur).

Pocher les ravioles dans une eau frémissante salée (10 g de gros sel/litre) pendant 1 min 30.
Au dernier moment, émulsionner le bouillon de volaille avec la crème liquide puis le verser sur les ravioles.

Vaporiser de l'huile de truffe blanche et servir.



Le plus du chef pour réussir votre Raviole de foie gras à l'huile de truffe blanche, bouillon de volaille

Vous pouvez réaliser ces ravioles à l'avance en les conservant au réfrigérateur, bien à plat dans un torchon légèrement humide.

Retrouvez cette recette en vidéo en cliquant sur http://www.atelierdeschefs.fr/fr/recette/3748-raviole-de-foie-gras-a-l-huile-de-truffe-blanche-bouillon-de-volaille.php ainsi que toutes les vidéos des Chefs de L'atelier des Chefs sur http://www.atelierdeschefs.fr

title: New Order of CRJ900 NextGen for Delta Air Lines
description:
We visited the Bombardier Mirabel facility, home and manufacturing base of the CRJ aircraft, on the day Delta Air Lines announced their firm order of 40 CRJ900 NextGen aircraft with an option to purchase 30 additional aircraft. Their excitement and heartfelt joy is truly palpable as they express their sentiments to long-time customer Delta Air Lines, and share with us what  it means for them to be part of the most successful regional jet program in the world.

Nouvelle commande de CRJ900 NextGen pour Delta Air Lines
Nous avons visité l'usine de Bombardier à Mirabel, site de l'assemblage final des appareils Bombardier CRJ, alors que Delta Air Lines annonçait une commande ferme de 40 avions CRJ900 NextGen avec une option d'achat de 30 appareils supplémentaires. Écoutez les réactions des employés quelques instants après l'annonce, leur excitation est palpable et ils expriment leurs sentiments envers Delta Air Lines, client de longue date des appareils CRJ. Ils partagent avec nous ce que signifie pour eux de faire partie du programme d'avions régionaux le plus populaire dans le monde.

title: Tokyo Auto Salon 2010 Perkenalkan Lamborghini Hijau Modifikasi
description:
Tokyo Auto Salon 2010 yang digelar minggu lalu di Tokyo, menampilkan model terbaru dari mobil hasil modifikasi. Ditengah-tengah krisis ekonomi global, pasar aksesoris mobil serta perlengkapannya justru menunjukkan gejala yang menggembirakan.

[Fumiaki Enomoto, Presiden, Tokyo Auto Salon]:
Jumlah mobil dalam event kami bertambah 12%, yang disebabkan oleh resesi. Orang-orang tidak bisa membeli mobil baru lagi, juga banyak anak muda yang cepat bosan akan mobil mereka. Jadi, bagian dalam dan luar mobil dirubah untuk memperbaharui perasaan. Ini arah yang kami lihat.

Untuk memperkenalkan konsep terbaru mobil sport FT-86, Toyota bekerjasama dengan Gazoo Racing untuk memproduksi si mentereng FT-86 G Sports Concept.

[Yuichi Tsurumoto, Manajer, Toyota]:
Dengan menambahkan turbo, kekuatan larinya bertambah. Di dalam sirkuit lomba, misalnya, kita bisa menikmati kontrol luncur yang disebut drifting. Kami membuatnya supaya anda bisa menikmati mobil yang penuh tenaga.

FT-86 diharapkan dapat mulai dipasarkan di tahun 2011, bertepatan dengan ulang tahun ke-25 dari Corolla AE86, yang merupakan generasi pertama dari FT-86.
Muncul pula mobil modifikasi lain dari Toyota, yaitu mobil hybrid Toyota Prius. Tak hanya ramah lingkungan, mobil yang satu ini juga didesain dengan kemewahan dan keanggunan.

[Kenichi Sato, Asisten Manajer, Design Group Toyota]:
Kalau anda lihat dari depan, bumpernya berbentuk seperti mulut-besar. Kami juga memodifikasi bagian lain. Kap mobil, atap dan pintu belakangnya terbuat dari karbon fiber. Kami telah merendahkan titik pusat gravitasi dan beratnya, kami juga memperhatikan aliran angin serta udara dari sisi ban mobil.

Perusahaan aftermarket dan layanan aksesori Liberty Walk menjalankan bisnis untuk memodifikasi Lamborghini. Mereka juga menciptakan buggy atau mobil-sepeda motor yang tampilannya mirip dengan Lamborghini.

[Naohito Otsu, Liberty Walk]:
Kami memodifikasi buggy beroda empat biasa dengan menambahkan material FRP. Ini adalah hasil modifikasi dari perusahaan kami.

Konsep Lamborghini Murcielago yang berwarna hijau dari Liberty Walk ini diinspirasi dari sebuah kata dalam bahasa Jepang, Kaeru, yang berarti katak, dan juga memiliki arti perubahan. Mobil super ini dilengkapi dengan modifikasi air-suspension yang dapat meninggikan dan merendahkan mobil.

[Keiichiro Sugita, Liberty Walk]:
Bos kami membayangkan katak hijau, dan ia memodifikasi mobil untuk melompat. Idenya adalah, mari kita rubah hidup, tetap bersemangat, melompat untuk kegembiraan. Ini adalah konsep dibelakang desainnya.

Ada lebih dari 600 mobil yang dipamerkan dalam Tokyo Auto Salon tahun ini. Setiap mobil memiliki cerita masing-masing dan hidup dengan kegembiraan dari hobi modifikasi.

Liliana Yap, NTD, Tokyo.

title: Travels with Timi Gustafson: Galapagos Islands
description:
The Galapagos Islands are a world apart - in almost every way. Frankly, I did not know what to expect when I embarked on this journey. In preparation, I read again Charles Darwin's "The Origin of Species." When I finally followed (literally) in his footsteps, I found myself overwhelmed and speechless in the face of such beauty, unspoiled by any form of civilization. This is the closest thing to time travel you can find on earth. 

Sadly, I'm used to wild animals running away from me, being afraid of all humans as potential predators. But not so here on these islands. In fact, I had to watch my every step, so I would not hurt nesting Albatross or Blue-footed Boobies who showed no inclination to get out of my way for the sake of self-preservation. More than once, I nearly squished an Iguana blending perfectly into the rocky landscape.

The best part of the Galapagos wildlife scene, of course, takes places under water. Bring your snorkel gear if you come here, because you are going to tango with the local seals, sea turtles and even the occasional shark (all harmless, I was told). 

The best (and in my opinion only) way to see the islands is to go by ship. I traveled comfortably to all the islands on the motor yacht "La Pinta." This recently renovated vessel offers comfortable accommodations, excellent food and good service. There are other yachts in the area, so you have a choice, even in high season. But I do recommend that you make all your travel arrangements at least one year before departure. 

Galapagos is well known as a unique travel destination and yet, due to careful park management (the islands are considered a wildlife refuge or park), there is no overcrowding. At any given day, most of the islands are as deserted as they were at the time of their discovery.

Of all the trips around the world I have taken so far, the Galapagos Islands stand out as a very special place, and my visit here will always remain an extraordinary experience.

-Solo admitimos en nuestra Escuela a niños apasionados por este deporte.

-Defendemos la idea del comienzo temprano en la práctica del motociclismo deportivo y admitimos alumnos a partir de los 2 años.

-Entendemos que los padres deben involucrarse en la formación deportiva de sus hijos.

-Nos basamos en que todos los esfuerzos en dedicación, trabajo y presupuesto, deben enfocarse hacia la creación de unos cimientos amplios y sólidos y no hacia la búsqueda de resultados.

-Los alumnos de nuestra Escuela practican y compiten en todas las especialidades posibles: Bike Trial, Trial, Motocross, Supermotard, minimotos, Velocidad, lo que les aporta una gran base técnica y mucha experiencia en situaciones de competición.

-Otro de los pilares básicos de nuestro método es la utilización de motos de serie. Está prohibido cualquier tipo de preparación o ventaja conseguida a base de fuertes inversiones.

-Nuestro objetivo es conseguir la formación sostenible, para cualquier economía

description:
Рок-оркестр «BREVIS» зібрав у Чернівцях небачений аншлаг
У Чернівецькій обласній філармонії відбувся концерт симфонічного оркестру «BREVIS». Колектив відомий цінителям музики не лише в Рівному, а також і за його межами. Музиканти Рівного, Луцька та Львова з успіхом презентують свої програми, адже вкладають у них душу у поєднанні з мистецьким виконанням творів та професійністю. У колективі -- 37 чоловік, репертуар -- класика, джаз, авангардова музика, зокрема Queen,‭ ‬Metallica,‭ ‬Deep Purple,‭ ‬Kiss,‭ ‬Pink Floyd,‭ ‬Scorpions,‭ ‬Nazareth,‭ ‬Bon Jovi,‭ ‬Muse,‭ ‬Depeche Mode,‭ ‬Майкла Джексона,‭ ‬AC/DC.
Як «BREVIS» потрапив у Чернівці і враження відвідувачів концерту -- дивіться у нашому ексклюзивному відеорепортажі.

title: Coway Su Arıtma Sistemleri
description:
Su, hiç şüphesiz yaşam kaynağımız. Buna rağmen, birçok insan içtiği suyun sağlığı için değerini önemsemiyor.
Su, insan vücudunun fonksiyonlarını yerine getirebilmesi için, sandığımızdan çok daha fazla gereklidir. Vücut ısısını düzenlemek, nefes alışımıza yardımcı olmak için soluduğumuz havayı nemlendirmek, sindirim sistemi, bağışıklık sistemi, beynimizdeki çeşitli hormonların üretimi ve toksinleri atmak gibi birçok yaşamsal sürecin gerçekleşmesinde suyun rolü büyüktür.
Günde ne kadar su içmeliyiz?
Vücudumuzun tüm ihtiyaçlarını tam olarak karşılamak için günde, 
2 - 2.5 litre su içmeliyiz. 
Bir günde ortalama olarak solunum yoluyla 600 ml, deri yoluyla 500 ml, idrar yoluyla 1400 ml su kaybederiz. Oysa ki, gıdalardan bunun sadece 500 ml'sini alabiliriz. Geri kalan ihtiyacımızı ancak su içerek karşılayabiliriz.

title: VICTOR MERZHANOV - TCHAIKOVSKY. The Seasons: July
description:
Victor Merzhanov, piano

Tchaikovsky. "The Seasons", op. 37-bis:
7. July (Song of the Reaper)

LAST RECITAL
Recorded at Great Hall of Moscow Conservatory on January 12, 2007.


http://Merzhanov.com


Victor Merzhanov was once called by a Swedish critic "a descendant of that line of great Russian-born pianists that began with Ziloty and Rachmaninov". Merzhanov graduated from the Moscow Conservatoire with distinction and his name was inscribed in its marble wall along with those of Scryabin and Rachmaninov. During his career he gave more tran 1500 recitals and concerts recitals with such conductors as Zanderling, Kondrashin, Gauk, Rozhdestvensky, Temirkanov, Svetlanov and many others. Merzhanov teaches at Moscow Conservatory since 1947.

Выдающийся русский пианист Виктор Мержанов, о котором шведский критик писал как о "достойном потомке великих пианистов, рожденных Россией, начиная с Зилоти и Рахманинова".За 50 лет сценической жизни он сыграл более 1500 концертов, в том числе с такими дирижерами, как К.Зандерлинг, К.Кондрашин, А.Гаук, Г.Рождественский, Ю.Темирканов, Е.Светланов.

Он имел блестящий успех во многих странах. В Италии его называли "настоящим волшебником, который поражает неповторимыми возможностями своих рук равно как и мудростью интерпретатора", в Польше писали, что "его игра открывает глаза на мир высочайшей гармонии, душевной красоты и благородной экспрессии, а его манера игры - образец недосягаемости"; в Америке отмечали "пластичность музыкального языка, необычную для исполнителей любой страны".

Виктор Мержанов родился в 1919 г. в Тамбове. В 1936 - 1941 гг. он учился в Московской консерватории по классу фортепиано у С.Фейнберга и по классу органа у А.Гедике. Окончил консерваторию с отличием, его имя занесено на мраморную стелу Московской консерватории и стоит в одном ряду с именами Скрябина, Рахманинова. 

В 1941 - 1945 гг. В.Мержанов служил в армии. После войны учился в аспирантуре Московской консерватории. В 1945 г. получил Первую премию на Всесоюзном конкурсе музыкантов- исполнителей, разделив ее с С.Рихтером. В 1949 г. стал лауреатом конкурса Шопена в Варшаве. С 1947 г. Виктор Мержанов - профессор Московской консерватории.

title: Karts K.S.V.-Saterland op Juniortrack TT-Circuit Assen.
description:
Zum ersten Mal TT Circuit, Eerste keer op TT Circuit.
Testtraining Karting.
Ongeveer 35 deelnemers hadden gehoor gegeven aan de oproep van de KSV(KartSportVerein)  -Saterland om zaterdag 13 juli 2013 als lid van deze verenging deel te nemen aan een circuittest op de TT-Circuit Assen  Junior Track. De KSV-Saterland organiseert wedstrijden in zowel Duitsland als Nederland voor het Duits/Nederlandse Kart Kampioenschap.
Onlangs heeft KSV Saterland een overeenkomst met het TT-Circuit Assen gesloten om het nieuwe junior motor circuit ook voor kartraces te gaan gebruiken.
Op de Juniortrack is een testtraining afgewerkt om te zien of de baan geschikt is voor kartwedstrijden. In het seizoen 2014 wil KSV Saterland de Juniortrack gebruiken voor kartraces.
Verleden jaar werd door de kartende broertjes Roy en Joran Haak en teambaas Willem van Dalen uit Westerbork al gewezen op de mogelijkheden voor karting op de TT-Circuit Juniortrack.
Op de testdag waren alle aanwezige rijders erg positief over de TT Circuit Juniortrack, al zullen er nog wel enige aanpassingen moeten komen. Maar deze zijn te overzien. 
Ook de KSV-Saterland was erg tevreden over deze accommodatie en sprak de wens uit in de toekomst samen met de TT organisatie dit junior circuit voor karts tot een succes te maken.

Test Training.
Über 35 Teilnehmer waren anwesend während einer Kart Training des KSV (Kart Sport Verein) Saterland, Samstag 13. Juli 2013 auf dem TT Circuit Assen Junior Track. Der TT Junior Titel ist neu und müsste getestet worden, um ihn zu benutzen, auch für Kart-Rennen
In der Saison 2014 will KSV Saterland die Junior Track benützen für Kart Rennen.
Am Testtag waren alle Fahrer sehr positiv über die Junior Track vom TT Circuit Assen. Es werden noch kleinere Anpassungen vorgenommen.
KSV-Saterland war auch sehr glücklich und will mit dem TT-Organisation, im Zukunft erfolgreich zusammen arbeiten. 

Muziek : The Cresters -- Assen Inst.

title: Top 4 Must Have apps for Moto E
tags: ['moto e', 'moto', 'must have apps', 'apps for moto e', 'basic apps', 'basic apps for moto e', 'moto e apps', 'smartphone', 'android kitkat', 'android', 'latest moto phone']
description:
Must have basic apps for Moto E

If Moto E is your first smartphone, then you have just entered a world full of amazing apps! The Android play store is full of all apps - if you need an app for something, it's probably there in your smartphone.

While there is a plethora of apps out there, there are a few basic apps that you must have on your Moto E to stay informed, productive and entertained.

Apps for Moto E:

1. Flipboard: It's a beautiful news app. Basically, you can choose your news interests - such as technology, design, photography, politics, sports, gadgets, etc. and Flipboard will make sure you receive news pertaining to only your interests. 
Flipboard makes sure that you only receive the most relevant and happening news feeds for your interests selected.
You can save articles for reading later, share an article with your friend and even build your own magazine.

2. Air Droid: 

Since you have just started using your smartphone, you must know how to transfer files on the Moto E to your computer and from your computer to the Moto E. 

Air Droid is an excellent app for transferring data. And it lets you transfer files such as photos, contacts, music and other files without any wire. Just ensure that your PC/Computer/Laptop is on the same wifi network as your phone. You need to make sure your phone is also on the wi-fi network. 

3. Microsoft Office Mobile:

Just as you'd expect, this app lets you open, edit and save microsoft office files such as word, excel and powerpoint files.
You can also use QuickOffice that comes loaded on the Moto E, however, with microsoft own app, it's much easier and faster.

4. Saavn: Free Bollywood Music

Saavn is the ultimate music app for Moto E. It lets you stream music online for free. You can listen to the latest bollywood tracks, albums and pop music. Simply search for the song you want to hear and tap on it to add it to the music player. The song would instantly start streaming. 

Please note, Saavn app requires an active internet connection. If you are on Wi-fi, then you won't be charged. However, if you are on 3G or 2G internet then you might be charged by the telecom operator depending on your internet package deal.

So these were the must have apps for Moto E.

Let me know if you think there is any other app that you must have app on the Moto E.

Thanks for watching guys.

title: Mozart Sonata No. 8 A minor (K.310) 1st movt
description:
Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart's Piano Sonata No. 8 in A minor, K. 310/300d, written in 
1778 is a sonata in three movements:

Allegro maestoso, common time
Andante cantabile con espressione, F major, 3/4
Presto, 2/4

The A minor sonata is the first of only two Mozart piano sonatas to have been composed in a minor key (the other being the No. 14 in C minor, K. 457). Written around the time of the death of Mozart's mother, it is one of the darkest of his sonatas. The last movement in particular has an obsessive, haunted quality about it, heightened near the end by the interruption of the relentless drive to the conclusion by repeated and chilling quiet falling passages.
